# TwinCAT CFC Migrator Safety

> All general migration safety rules are defined in `twincat3-migration-safety.mdc`. This file adds CFC-specific notes only.

## CFC-Specific Notes

- TODO markers use the format `TODO [CFC Migration]`
- CFC has no network concept; all statements are placed in a single network
- Execution order is derived from XML serialization order (see Rule 11 in migration-safety)
- Operators (AND, OR, EQ, etc.) are inlined as nested ST expressions
- The tool skips NWL/FBD, SFC, and IL implementations automatically
